Anthony VERDONI, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Vincent J. D'ELIA, Esq., D'Elia & McCarthy, Defendants-Petitioners,
and
John and Jane Does 1-10 (Fictitiously Named Parties), Defendants. C-735 September Term 2018
082256 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 21, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004976-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
